      "span_text": "With the release of the genome sequence, a genomewide mutagenesis approach has been developed for P. aeruginosa. This genomic analysis and mapping by in vitro transposition (GAMBIT) technology relies on allelic exchange mutagenesis to detect essential P. aeruginosa genes [CITATION_1] ."
